Graphs and summaries update in real time to enable insightful bidding. Time Machine's recommendations are provided every hour, for every ad group, to highlight the optimal combination of bid type and bid price. <br><br>

All of this is done through a responsive web interface that makes our platform accessible on all devices, so that you can stay connected on the go.  </p>
																
