							<p class="tall">
								Take full advantage of savings by either using your remaining campaign budget to further boost goals, or re-allocate that campaign budget to other marketing needs. SocialSway can automatically pause campaigns once goals are met so that you can make the choice and maximize your savings.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6">
